commit.title: Micromega: more robust (still fragile) generation of cutting planes
commit.message:
Micromega: more robust (still fragile) generation of cutting planes

The cutting planes are now generated from an optimal Simplex tableau.
Previous naive cuts could loop forever or miss a cutting plance.
(More work is necessary to ensure completeness and convergence.)
